{"tid":43791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人會同自己唔中意嘅人拍拖？","createTime":"2016-12-17T17:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T14:31:37.000Z","uid":11045,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c71d03d561858d3db407c6c5cffcf8722dbd35d8","tid":43791,"uid":11045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"成日覺得佢根本唔緊張我唔關心我<br />\n我一唔開心佢就去訓教唔理<br />\n又開口酸有UGC有HALL住<br />\n成日同女cchat又唔比人睇傾咩<br />\n係街剩係識玩手機<br />\n兩個人無野好傾<br />\n我係咁揾話題佢理都唔理我<br />\n前排仲過份 我問佢無番工夠錢洗咩？<br />\n佢叫我做PTGF 我問佢係咪唔介意比其他男仔掂<br />\n佢竟然答唔介意 仲問如果係收咩價<br />\n佢其實做左好多野傷我心 都原諒佢<br />\n但最近因為PTGF我下定決心分手<br />\n唔好意思1999<br />\n但佢其實係咪無中意過我"},{"pid":"8f60692ed7bfeeb83d26182a13904c6cc6b3f714","tid":43791,"uid":66751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"你估我同你fall in love 呀？"},{"pid":"28ef2a062971375262d6549d61829a274f52047c","tid":43791,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"如果我話唔係樓主係咪會好過少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實睇清一個男仔交唔交得過由做朋友既時候已經可以睇到，但無奈時下太多人過於盲目<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874e4225e3a9c9eaed76a729c6a307c378402ead","tid":43791,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果係小甜甜，我可能會屈服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cdd1202aad7d4d7caa8b102c18ee2fb38ae4d9","tid":43791,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"係咪佢唔識表達<br />\n但如果拍拖咁痛苦就放手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ce41b114ccdace8dba45fe0ef5e1e5d2e517b1","tid":43791,"uid":15172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"分手啦,呢啲人唔好要佢喇<br />\n等我做你下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b2e467696acfb34dd6a2194cd004db