47df","tid":43791,"uid":18616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心問 你地點開始</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曖昧左一陣 嗌左次交 就確認關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n我直接簡單咁問<br />\n邊個開口/主動話一齊<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野叫確認關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扑左野呀"},{"pid":"bacc67f529cd293ffae1f89a4711db5a4ea355ad","tid":43791,"uid":67016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb73835703b68d51605d679fd2a9337b899679e","tid":43791,"uid":18616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"你應該轉個問題再問一次<br />\n<br />\n其實有無人會同唔中意(唔無太中意)自己既人一齊<br />\n<br />\n既然你都知佢唔係中意你 甚至一開始已知<br />\n都頂到成年<br />\n<br />\n與其你想問對方咁係咩心態<br />\n不如你攪清楚自己咩心態仲好"},{"pid":"c72f7a2d0dba045c3ad1b7dda8c4a8333a7e8851","tid":43791,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"咁都要問弓你智商幾多？讀屎片？"},{"pid":"6173f720c0127e702fd1c9da49b664cd2a7675a4","tid":43791,"uid":18616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"我直覺覺得<br />\n樓主所謂既確認關係應該係攪左野<br />\n對方只係當佢免費肉洞"},{"pid":"b2318f4d9d8ec13eb52be65ad75a5e6ca77515f7","tid":43791,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"當然有，有個朋友淨係想同條女扑嘢， 冇打算一齊，只係因為條女表白又唔好意思拒絕,最後一齊左條女唔俾搞，佢已經好想分手對條女勁冷淡"},{"pid":"16d78a07ad3c8d933d5b0c22ecf9cda311ed89d5","tid":43791,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"好誇張wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b448e6c1a7ba23b5a0f0287cb10fd5938d443ba","tid":43791,"uid":27298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以搵我傾下 我都試過<br />\n做到隻狗咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低